reviews.review_text: might as well lil red rooster rocks  brent  just blows the hammond  up to be in ear shot live was a real treat drove from so cal  first midwest shows the arena was like a old hockey arena  like a bowl  sound  was prefect   small place  might as well knock my socks off  or was it the rose  purple  jell  or the roses     the tour got better  got to see the country a place you never been   i was only 19  got all the bud i could buy loaded up vw van with big sal  we smoke all the way there  and blame it on  boys on tour
